# Implementation Plan - SOP Overhaul for ACCI Fellowship

The goal is to refine the `STATEMENT_OF_PURPOSE.md` to meet the **500-word limit** while maximizing its impact and alignment with the **Africa Climate Collaborative Initiative (ACCI)** theme of **Sustainable Agriculture**.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The current SOP is **908 words**, and the fellowship requires a maximum of **500 words**. This requires a significant structural condensation. I will focus on merging technical skills with academic achievements to save space.

## Proposed Changes

### [Statement of Purpose](file:///c:/YERBO/Desktop/Courage/precision%20agriculture/STATEMENT_OF_PURPOSE.md)

#### [MODIFY] [STATEMENT_OF_PURPOSE.md](file:///c:/YERBO/Desktop/Courage/precision%20agriculture/STATEMENT_OF_PURPOSE.md)
- **Introduction:** Sharpen the focus on the "Sustainable Agriculture" theme and the dual pressure of climate change and mining in Ghana.
- **Background Section:** Merge academic excellence (First Class) with leadership (Teaching Assistant/YouthMappers) into one high-impact paragraph.
- **Research Alignment:** Explicitly frame the 1D-CNN and Variable-Rate Application (VRA) as a **Climate-Smart Agricultural (CSA)** practice that optimizes mitigation (N2O reduction) and resilience (yield stability).
